------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sample file to make PCM file (WAV file)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Summary:

Sample source codes to make a PCM file (440kHz, two sec).
Note that this sample does not take care of byte order.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage:

$ make
$ ./wavsample
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Files:

wavsample.cc
  A source code.

test.wav:
  An output file (440kHz, two sec).
------------------------------------------------------------------------
